cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE

This paper discusses the techniques and algorithms used for distributed training of deep neural networks, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as the paper specifically focuses on distributed training. The paper also mentions ImageNet, which is a popular dataset used in computer vision, so cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also a likely category. Additionally, the paper discusses the advancements in deep learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
